data.description: Fantastic investment opportunity for savvy investors or creative individuals longing to design their dream home. This property boasts a generously sized family room with built-ins, a cozy brick fireplace, and a wet bar. Hosting family gatherings is a breeze in the spacious formal dining area. Enjoy the outdoors in the oversized sunroom with sliding glass doors that open to the backyard. A private study provides the perfect workspace for remote professionals. Upstairs, you'll find all bedrooms accompanied by two full bathrooms. The primary suite is exceptionally spacious, complemented by a large walk-in closet and vanity area. The backyard is a gem, featuring an extended patio for outdoor enjoyment. Unleash your vision and seize this excellent opportunity!
